{
  "chapter": 48,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙在郭家山庄与严平比武获胜后，随李牧同行。李牧深忧赵国国运，感叹匈奴长期寇边使赵国无力扩张，虽为名将却只能守成。项少龙被其悲天悯人的精神打动，透露赵穆可能是楚国间谍的线索，李牧大喜愿配合行动。回到乌氏城堡，乌应元严厉指出赵国注定灭亡，乌家唯一出路是依附秦国，催促项少龙尽快将嬴政母子送回咸阳。项少龙沐浴时与婷芳氏、乌廷芳温存片刻，随后带滕翼、荆俊夜探朱姬居所。他躲在柜中意外发现赵国大夫郭开竟是朱姬的情人，朱姬正以色相诱使郭开帮她逃回秦国。郭开敷衍推脱，朱姬趁其熟睡开柜取衣，项少龙现身表明奉吕不韦之命来救她。朱姬欣然接受，约定明晚再详商逃亡计划。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们今天是忍无可忍，孤注一掷，藉妮夫人的事与赵穆作最后的周旋。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我和相国一直留心你，少龙你是我大赵这数代人里难得的人才，且是这么年轻。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假设今天大王仍要维护赵穆，少龙立即离开赵国，到别处闯天下，不要像我们般瞎守着这完全没有希望的国家。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_mu",
      "text": "我们得到了《秘录》，为何大将军仍这么悲观？我看大赵的人丁正兴旺起来，只要再多几个年头，便能恢复原气……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你对国事认识尚浅，纵没有长平之战的大伤元气，我们亦有先天的缺陷，就是不断寇边的匈奴，使我们为了应付他们，国力长期损耗。所以各国中唯我大赵人丁最是单薄，虽是名将辈出，但建国后从来只有守成的份儿，没有扩张的能力。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_mu",
      "text": "大将军既看清楚这点，为何恋栈赵境不去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人非草木，孰能无情，我长期守卫北疆与匈奴作战，和边塞的住民建立了深厚的感情，若我弃他们而去，凶残狠毒的匈奴人还有谁能抵挡，我怎忍心让他们任人屠戮？唉！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_mu",
      "text": "大将军可否把上书大王一事，推迟两天？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你似乎有点把握，究竟是什么妙招？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你真行，我们从未曾想过由这点入手对付赵穆，我还会在邯郸留上几天，让我们紧密联络，配合上书的时间。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_mu",
      "speaker_name": "李牧",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你仍是血气方刚，很难抵受诱惑，你须紧记酒色害人，纵是铁汉，也受不起那种日以继夜的销蚀，少龙定要切记。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "图先刚派人和我联络，说吕不韦的形势相当不妙，他在秦国的敌人正利用疏不间亲之理，在庄襄王前拨弄是非排斥他，庄襄王为人又优柔寡断，说不定会被打动，所以把嬴政母子送返咸阳一事刻不容缓，有她母子二人在庄襄王身边，吕不韦的地位可稳如山岳，甚至可坐上相国之位，否则连我们的希望也破灭。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "可否拖迟几天，看看扳倒赵穆一事是否有转机？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知少龙恨不得把赵穆碎尸万段，但这始终是私人恩怨，少龙应以大局为重，现在乌家的命运已落在你肩头上，一个不好，势是堡破人亡之局。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "若扳倒赵穆，大赵或仍有可为……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这只是妄想，就算杀掉赵穆，在孝成王这种昏君手上，赵家乃注定是亡国之奴，赵太子亦非好材料。乌家唯一出路，是依附大秦，才有希望。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知少龙智计过人，不知对送回嬴政母子的事，有什么头绪？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "现在时间尚早，待我休息一会儿，便去找朱姬，只要能说服她，事情才有望成功。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙在想什么呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是想着雅姊和倩公主！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "和你们两个美人在一起，怎会想起其他女人。我只是因今晚有要事去办，不能陪你们，所以才心中苦恼。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "陶公刚通知我们了，项郎放心去吧！我们两人会乖乖地等你回来，噢！忘了告诉你，自你到大梁去后，婷姊每晚都和芳儿同床共寝，说亲密话儿，今晚我们姊妹就在榻上等你回来。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到严平都不是你对手，真希望你能挫挫那赵霸的威风。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说她是连晋那坏蛋的情人之一，你杀了连晋，她自然恨你入骨哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "荆俊这小子定是心中暗恨，因为我把他从有女人的温暖被窝中抓了出来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他敢？我警诫过他，若太荒唐的话，就把他赶回家去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到里面这么大！我找到朱姬的住处了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "我们去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们就在这里为你接应把风，若见形势不对，荆俊会扮鸟叫通知你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "婢女甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最怕就是他了，每次来夫人都不用睡觉，累得我们要在旁伺候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "婢女乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人平时话也不多半句，见到他却像有说不完的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "婢女甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总好过服侍那个色鬼，身体都不行了，还要靠讨厌的玩意发泄，香姊给他一连三晚弄得只剩下半条人命。唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "人家托你的事，办得如何？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "现在局势不明，仍未是回秦的时刻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "有什么不明朗的，现在异人登上王位，只要我们母子返回咸阳，政儿就是继承王位的储君，还有什么好顾忌的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "不要！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "春宵一刻值千金，难得有这机会，来！到帐内再说。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "你只是对人家身体有兴趣，一点不关心妾身的心事。你说吧！为何答应人家的事却不做？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "你不知我已做了很多功夫吗？只是现在庄襄王刚登位，各方面看得你们很紧，兼且吕不韦现在地位不稳，随时有坍台的危险，无论怎样计算，你也绝不应于此时偷回咸阳去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "来吧！天气这么冷，有什么地方比被窝更舒服呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "你先到帐内去，我落了妆便来陪你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我是项少龙，奉吕不韦之命来找你！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知你是谁，因为赵穆现在最想除去的人是你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "希望你清楚乌家和吕先生的关系，他派图先来和我们接触，要尽快把你们母子弄回咸阳去。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有图先来我就放心，你们有什么计划？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "首先要和你取得联络，了解情况，才能定下逃亡的细节，我……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "明晚再来！我等你。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
